import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar'
import Notification from '../components/Notification'
const Container = styled.div`
    
`

const ProductList = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Notification/>
        <Navbar/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default ProductList
